Here are some comands you could use.. Edit Commands However You Need * Replace ComPort with your port number
Read Nor: NORwayy.py ComPort dump nand.bin
Write Nand With Diff: NANDway.py ComPort 0 diffwrite "mydump0.bin" "mydump0-diff.txt"
Erase 16MB Nand: NORwayy.py ComPort erase
Flash Teensy Firmware: teensy -mmcu=at90usb1286 -w NORway.hex
Compare Files: FC File1.bin File2.bin
